<plot>Have you ever had someone tell you that you're empty? Margaret Carson has. It's almost her 25th birthday, and she's just been dumped. Now completely alone, Margaret begins to drift between troubling dreams and reality. In an attempt to pull herself together, she prepares to throw the party of her life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?016169</url></doc>
